reviews.review_text:
Very Nice GEM 
Wonderful recording of a highly decent show. The Bird Song, Crazy Fingers and Stella Blue are all kaptivating keepers.

Performance doesn't merit a 5, but I enjoyed it so much personally that I gave it a 5.
